--------------------------------------------------------
OpenHPI View 2.0
--------------------------------------------------------

This is a WxPython based End User Interface which interacts with the OpenHPI (Implementation of the Service Availability Forum's Hardware Platform Interface Specification B.02.01 ).

The following components are supported:
* Hpiview2


Feedback, as always, is welcome and encouraged:
openhpi-devel@lists.sourceforge.net

---------------------------------------------------------
PREREQUISITES
---------------------------------------------------------
The following software is required to run OpenHPI View 2.0

openhpi  >=  2.8
wxpython >=  2.6
python   >=  2.5

---------------------------------------------------------
BUILD / INSTALLATION
---------------------------------------------------------

1. Untar the hpiview package to a directory
2. Run the ./setup.py

This should install the hpiview2.
 
 --------------------------------------------------------
 RUNNING THE APPLICATION
 --------------------------------------------------------
 
 1. Use "hpiview2" to execute the application.
